# Agent Frameworks & Patterns
## 2-Week Nanodegree Module

### üéØ **Module Overview**
This self-paced 2-week module provides comprehensive instruction on building production-ready AI agents using modern frameworks and implementing the five core agentic patterns: Reflection, Tool Use, ReAct, Planning, and Multi-Agent Collaboration. Through hands-on tutorials and progressive implementation, you'll develop skills to create intelligent, adaptable agents using both bare-metal approaches and established frameworks.

